---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'quick-verdict', text: 'Quick Verdict', level: 2 },
  { id: 'comparison-table', text: 'Side-by-Side Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'img', text: 'IMG Global', level: 2 },
  { id: 'safetywing', text: 'SafetyWing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'cigna', text: 'Cigna Global', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'teacher-needs', text: 'Teacher-Specific Considerations', level: 2 },
  { id: 'best-for', text: 'Which Is Best For You?', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'FAQs', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { href: '/insurance-for/teachers-abroad', text: 'Teacher Insurance Guide' },
  { href: '/best/expat-health-insurance', text: 'Best Expat Insurance' },
  { href: '/providers/img-global', text: 'IMG Global Review' },
  { href: '/providers/safetywing', text: 'SafetyWing Review' },
  { href: '/providers/cigna-global', text: 'Cigna Global Review' },
];

const mainComparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'img', header: 'IMG Global' },
  { key: 'safetywing', header: 'SafetyWing' },
  { key: 'cigna', header: 'Cigna Global' },
];

const mainComparisonRows = [
  { feature: 'Monthly Cost (30)', img: '$120-200', safetywing: '$45', cigna: '$300-450' },
  { feature: 'Coverage Limit', img: '$1M-5M', safetywing: '$250,000', cigna: 'Unlimited' },
  { feature: 'Contract Duration', img: 'Annual', safetywing: 'Monthly', cigna: 'Annual' },
  { feature: 'Home Summer Visits', img: 'Up to 30 days', safetywing: '30 days/90', cigna: 'Up to 180 days' },
  { feature: 'Routine Care', img: 'Optional', safetywing: 'Not covered', cigna: 'Included' },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', img: 'Limited', safetywing: 'Crisis only', cigna: 'Comprehensive' },
  { feature: 'Pre-existing Conditions', img: 'Limited options', safetywing: 'Excluded', cigna: 'Can be covered' },
  { feature: 'Visa Letters', img: 'Yes', safetywing: 'Yes', cigna: 'Yes' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'profile', header: 'Profile' },
  { key: 'img', header: 'IMG Global' },
  { key: 'safetywing', header: 'SafetyWing' },
  { key: 'cigna', header: 'Cigna Global' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { profile: 'New teacher (25)', img: '$100-150/mo', safetywing: '$42/mo', cigna: '$280-380/mo' },
  { profile: 'Experienced teacher (35)', img: '$150-220/mo', safetywing: '$45/mo', cigna: '$350-480/mo' },
  { profile: 'Teacher + spouse', img: '$280-400/mo', safetywing: '$90/mo', cigna: '$650-900/mo' },
  { profile: 'Family (2 adults + child)', img: '$400-600/mo', safetywing: '$135/mo', cigna: '$900-1,200/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="IMG vs SafetyWing vs Cigna for Teachers Abroad | 2025 Comparison"
  description="Compare health insurance for international teachers: IMG's mid-tier coverage, SafetyWing's budget option, and Cigna's premium plans. Expert analysis for TEFL, IB, and international school teachers."
  headline="IMG vs SafetyWing vs Cigna: Insurance for Teachers Abroad"
  subheadline="From first-year TEFL teachers to veteran international school educators—find the right health coverage for your teaching career overseas."
  heroImage="/images/pages/provider-card-generic.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes"
  ctaButtonHref="/get-quotes"
>
  <section id="quick-verdict" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Quick Verdict</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-800 mb-2">IMG Global</h3>
        <p class="text-primary-700 mb-3">Best Mid-Range</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">Solid coverage at reasonable prices for established teachers. Good balance of limits, routine care options, and affordability.</p>
        <a href="/providers/img-global" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-primary-700 transition text-sm" style="color: white !important;">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">SafetyWing</h3>
        <p class="text-purple-700 mb-3">Best Budget</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">Perfect for first-year TEFL teachers on tight budgets. Basic emergency coverage at $45/month with flexible monthly billing.</p>
        <a href="/providers/safetywing" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-purple-700 transition text-sm" style="color: white !important;">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Cigna Global</h3>
        <p class="text-green-700 mb-3">Best Premium</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">Comprehensive coverage for career international teachers. School-quality benefits when your employer doesn't provide adequate insurance.</p>
        <a href="/providers/cigna-global" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition text-sm" style="color: white !important;">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="comparison-table" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Side-by-Side Comparison</h2>
    <ComparisonTable columns={mainComparisonColumns} rows={mainComparisonRows} />
  </section>

  <section id="img" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">IMG Global</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Mid-Range Price</span>
      <span class="bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Good Limits</span>
      <span class="bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Teacher-Friendly</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">IMG Global is the sweet spot for international teachers—offering real insurance coverage without premium pricing. Their Global Medical Insurance provides $1M-5M in coverage, adequate for serious medical events anywhere in the world. This is the upgrade from SafetyWing when you're ready for comprehensive protection.</p>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Outpatient care is available as an add-on, covering the routine visits and prescriptions teachers need throughout the year. Home country coverage during summer breaks (up to 30 days) means you're protected during visits home. IMG is particularly popular among TEFL teachers in Asia and the Middle East.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Teacher Strengths</h4>
        <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Affordable mid-range pricing</li>
          <li>• $1M-5M coverage limits</li>
          <li>• Optional routine care</li>
          <li>• Summer home visits included</li>
          <li>• Visa letter provided</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Considerations</h4>
        <ul class="text-amber-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Annual commitment required</li>
          <li>• Limited mental health coverage</li>
          <li>• Pre-existing conditions limited</li>
          <li>• Home visits capped at 30 days</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/providers/img-global" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get IMG Quote</a>
  </section>

  <section id="safetywing" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">SafetyWing</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">$45/Month</span>
      <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Monthly Billing</span>
      <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Flexible</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">SafetyWing is the go-to for first-year TEFL teachers and those on limited budgets. At $45/month, it's affordable even on entry-level teaching salaries. The month-to-month billing is perfect for one-year contracts—if you don't renew or return home, you simply stop paying.</p>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Coverage is basic but covers emergencies: hospitalization, surgery, and emergency care up to $250,000. It won't cover routine doctor visits or pre-existing conditions, so plan to pay cash for minor healthcare. For young, healthy teachers, this trade-off often makes sense financially.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Teacher Strengths</h4>
        <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Lowest cost option ($45/mo)</li>
          <li>• Monthly flexibility</li>
          <li>• No annual commitment</li>
          <li>• Quick online signup</li>
          <li>• Home country visits included</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Limitations</h4>
        <ul class="text-amber-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• $250K limit (lower)</li>
          <li>• No routine care</li>
          <li>• Pre-existing excluded</li>
          <li>• Crisis-only mental health</li>
          <li>• May not satisfy all visa requirements</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/providers/safetywing" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get SafetyWing Quote</a>
  </section>

  <section id="cigna" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Cigna Global</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Premium Coverage</span>
      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Full Benefits</span>
      <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Career Teachers</span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Cigna Global is the choice for career international educators who want top-tier coverage. Unlimited medical benefits, comprehensive mental health (crucial given teaching stress), and 180 days of home country coverage for extended summer breaks. This is school-quality insurance you can take with you between postings.</p>

    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Pre-existing conditions can eventually be covered through moratorium periods—important if you've developed conditions during your teaching career. The premium price reflects premium benefits; for teachers at top-tier international schools who supplement inadequate employer coverage, Cigna provides peace of mind.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Teacher Strengths</h4>
        <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Unlimited coverage</li>
          <li>• Comprehensive mental health</li>
          <li>• 180 days home visits</li>
          <li>• Pre-existing can be covered</li>
          <li>• Portable between schools/countries</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Considerations</h4>
        <ul class="text-amber-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>• Highest premiums</li>
          <li>• Annual commitment</li>
          <li>• May exceed budget for new teachers</li>
          <li>• Overkill for one-year contracts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/providers/cigna-global" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
  </section>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Teacher Coverage Quotes"
    description="Get quotes tailored to your teaching destination and contract length."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/get-quotes"
  />

  <section id="pricing" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Pricing Comparison</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">Coverage costs for different teacher profiles:</p>
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-4">*IMG and Cigna prices include comprehensive inpatient + outpatient. SafetyWing is emergency medical only. All prices exclude US coverage.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="teacher-needs" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Teacher-Specific Considerations</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-3">Contract Types</h3>
        <ul class="text-neutral-700 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong>TEFL (1 year):</strong> SafetyWing or IMG</li>
          <li>• <strong>IB Schools (2+ years):</strong> IMG or Cigna</li>
          <li>• <strong>International Schools:</strong> Supplement employer coverage</li>
          <li>• <strong>University Lecturers:</strong> IMG or Cigna</li>
          <li>• <strong>Summer Programs:</strong> SafetyWing monthly</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-3">School-Provided Insurance</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-4">Questions to ask employers:</p>
        <ul class="text-neutral-700 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• What are the coverage limits?</li>
          <li>• Does it cover home country visits?</li>
          <li>• What about mental health?</li>
          <li>• Is family coverage included?</li>
          <li>• What happens if I leave?</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">Popular Teaching Destinations</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">Asia</h4>
          <ul class="text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• China: Visa requires insurance</li>
            <li>• South Korea: EPIK provides basic</li>
            <li>• Japan: JET program coverage</li>
            <li>• Thailand: Buy your own</li>
            <li>• Vietnam: Employer varies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">Middle East</h4>
          <ul class="text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• UAE: Schools usually provide</li>
            <li>• Saudi Arabia: Employer required</li>
            <li>• Qatar: Package typically included</li>
            <li>• Kuwait: Supplementing common</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">Europe/Americas</h4>
          <ul class="text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Spain: Visa requires insurance</li>
            <li>• France: Assistantship varies</li>
            <li>• Latin America: Usually buy own</li>
            <li>• Czech Republic: Visa specific</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="best-for" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Which Is Best For You?</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-primary-50 border-l-4 border-primary-600 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-primary-800 mb-2">Choose IMG Global if:</h3>
        <ul class="text-primary-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• You're an established teacher (2+ years)</li>
          <li>• You want real coverage without premium prices</li>
          <li>• Routine care access matters</li>
          <li>• You're planning multi-year contracts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-600 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">Choose SafetyWing if:</h3>
        <ul class="text-purple-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• You're a first-year TEFL teacher</li>
          <li>• Budget is tight ($45/mo works)</li>
          <li>• You're young and healthy</li>
          <li>• Flexibility matters (one-year contract)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-600 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">Choose Cigna Global if:</h3>
        <ul class="text-green-700 space-y-1">
          <li>• You're a career international educator</li>
          <li>• Mental health coverage is important</li>
          <li>• You have pre-existing conditions</li>
          <li>• You want portable, long-term coverage</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="faqs" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Will my school provide health insurance?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">It depends. International schools often include health coverage in packages, but quality varies widely. Many TEFL positions, especially in private language centers, don't include insurance. Always clarify before signing a contract, and consider supplementing inadequate employer coverage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">What happens during summer break?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">This is critical for teachers. SafetyWing covers 30 days per 90-day period in your home country. IMG covers up to 30 days of home visits. Cigna offers up to 180 days—best for teachers who spend entire summers home. Check your plan's home country limitations carefully.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Can I get a visa letter from these insurers?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Yes, all three provide visa compliance letters confirming your coverage. However, some countries (like China or Czech Republic) have specific insurance requirements that not all plans meet. Verify your destination's visa requirements before choosing a plan.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Should I keep coverage between contracts?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">If you're a career teacher moving between schools, maintaining continuous coverage is valuable. It prevents new waiting periods and pre-existing condition exclusions. SafetyWing's month-to-month structure works well for gaps; Cigna's portability is ideal for long-term careers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="bg-neutral-100 rounded-lg p-6 text-sm text-neutral-600">
    <p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Insurance pricing and coverage vary by age, location, and plan level. Teacher-provided benefits differ significantly by school and country. Always verify current coverage and visa compliance directly with providers before purchasing. This comparison is for informational purposes only.</p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
